{"tid":547041,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂拍板(再)將孖寶兄弟搬上大銀幕","createTime":"2018-02-01T05:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T07:30:51.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb5f33815ba2b78fa4b86b49d234cfafa3192ff","tid":547041,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"任天堂(Nintendo)決定與環球影業(Universal Pictures)動畫製作公司Illumination聯手，製作旗下吸金電玩角色「孖寶兄弟」(Super Mario，另譯超級馬里奧)的動畫電影。<br />\n<br />\n任天堂發表新聞稿指出，其高層宮本茂(Shigeru Miyamoto)將與Illumination創始人Chris Meledandri合作拍攝一部電影，由任天堂和環球影業負責投資。電影發行將由環球影業負責。<br />\n<br />\n任天堂未透露這部電影將於何時上映。不過，在《超級馬里奧：奧德賽》在任天堂Switch平台大獲成功之後，遊戲的粉絲正情緒高漲。根據任天堂數據顯示，自去年10月發布後，這款遊戲自今賣出超過900萬份。外界相信，當「孖寶兄弟」動畫電影正式上映時，有可能會進一步推高該公司相關產品的銷量。"},{"pid":"fa9a5e455f526a873871d2f4d5c722de98cbbbb4","tid":547041,"uid":81397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"Illumination<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0521983383168680193e246dd9828e59994e5348","tid":547041,"uid":36509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa9a5e455f526a873871d2f4d5c722de98cbbbb4","tid":547041,"uid":81397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"Illumination<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"推啲蘑菇人做minions<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8bf0ed5aad8b7a01682adcd60e421cd85c76e1","tid":547041,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"當年睇完，唔敢同人講，真係俾人笑到面黃"},{"pid":"1ee80342e927f866b3c3b571d0c5e8d425e6e0dc","tid":547041,"uid":120859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T07:30:51.000Z","msg":"真人版就睇"}]}